    "Recall formula:Recall ¼ TP TP þ FNð11ÞF1 score value: Calculates the harmonic weight of the precision and recall values.",
    "F1 score formula:F1 ¼ 2 Precision Â Recall Precision þ Recallð12ÞmAP value: The average precision (AP) value is a popular metric for object detection detectors.",
    "The AP value calculates an average value for the recall value from 0 to 1.",
    "The mAP value is a value that gives the average of all AP values as a single number.",
